Herter likely refers to 
<taxonomicName family="Verbenaceae" genus="S." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="S. pseudogracile" order="Solanales" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" rank="species" species="pseudogracile">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">S. pseudogracile</emphasis>
